data.text: When William L Gibson was born on 3 September 1705, in Allhallows, Cumberland, England, United Kingdom, his father, William Gibson, was 39 and his mother, Jane Thomas, was 28. He married Margaret Jane Spurgeon about 1728, in Newton, Cumberland, Tennessee, United States. They were the parents of at least 5 sons and 7 daughters. He died in January 1771, in Newton, Cumberland, Tennessee, United States, at the age of 65.
